OL,3,CWhat are the charges against
OL,4,CManchester City and what is at stake?
OL,6,FAn independent commission hearing to
OL,7,Fexamine 115 charges laid by the
OL,8,FPremier League against Manchester City
OL,9,Fwill finally begin on Monday, 16
OL,10,FSeptember.
OL,12,FThe club is accused of bending
OL,13,Ffinancial rules, following a four-year
OL,14,Finvestigation, with City facing a
OL,15,Fhefty points deduction or even
OL,16,Fexpulsion from the league if found
OL,17,Fguilty.
