OL,3,CWhat are the charges against
OL,4,CManchester City and what is at stake?
OL,6,FReams of evidence will be sifted
OL,7,Fthrough over 10 weeks, in what has
OL,8,Fbeen described as one of the biggest
OL,9,Ftrials in sporting history.
OL,11,FWhat are the charges against
OL,12,FManchester City?
OL,14,FThe 115 charges against City relate to
OL,15,Fthe requirement to accurately report
OL,16,Ffinancial information.
