OL,3,CWhat are the charges against
OL,4,CManchester City and what is at stake?
OL,6,FThis includes the submission of
OL,7,Fdetails of manager and player pay
OL,8,Finformation within the relevant
OL,9,Fcontracts, a club's responsibility to
OL,10,Fadhere to UEFA's Financial Fair Play
OL,11,Fregulations and to the league's own
OL,12,Fprofitability and sustainability
OL,13,Fregulations.
OL,15,FCity is also accused of failing to co-
OL,16,Foperate with the league's
OL,17,Finvestigation. In all, there are
OL,18,Fcharges relating to every season
OL,19,Fbetween 2009-10 and 2022-23.
OL,21,FHow did this come about?
