OL,3,CWhat are the charges against
OL,4,CManchester City and what is at stake?
OL,6,FThe Premier League opened an
OL,7,Finvestigation into City way back in
OL,8,F2018 and, after a number of legal
OL,9,Fdelays, charges were finally laid in
OL,10,FFebruary 2023.
OL,12,FManchester City were then referred to
OL,13,Fan independent commission.
OL,15,FWhat have City said?
OL,17,FThe club issued a statement
OL,18,Fstrenuously denying the allegations on
OL,19,Fthe day the charges were brought.
