OL,3,CWhat are the charges against
OL,4,CManchester City and what is at stake?
OL,6,FIt "welcomed the opportunity" for an
OL,7,Findependent commission "to impartially
OL,8,Fconsider the comprehensive body of
OL,9,Firrefutable evidence that exists in
OL,10,Fsupport of our position".
OL,12,FIt added: "As such, we look forward to
OL,13,Fthis matter being put to rest once and
OL,14,Ffor all."
OL,16,FWhy is this so significant?
OL,18,FSo much is at stake. City face a huge
OL,19,Fpoints deduction or even expulsion
OL,20,Ffrom the league if found guilty of the
OL,21,Fserial cheating they are accused of.
