OL,3,CWhat are the charges against
OL,4,CManchester City and what is at stake?
OL,6,FIf City's position is vindicated, on
OL,7,Fthe other hand, it will lead to
OL,8,Fserious questions about the Premier
OL,9,FLeague's ability to effectively govern
OL,10,Fits clubs and enforce financial
OL,11,Fregulations, at a time when football
OL,12,Fis set to become subject to
OL,13,Findependent regulation.
OL,15,FHas Pep Guardiola said anything about
OL,16,Fthe case?
OL,18,FThe City boss has welcomed the start
OL,19,Fof the trial.
