OL,3,CWhat are the charges against
OL,4,CManchester City and what is at stake?
OL,6,FGuardiola was speaking at a press
OL,7,Fconference to preview Saturday's home
OL,8,Fclash with Brentford, telling
OL,9,Freporters "everyone is innocent until
OL,10,Fguilt is proven."
OL,12,F"Justice is there in modern democratic
OL,13,Fcountries, so wait for the decision.
OL,14,FIt's not much more complicated than
OL,15,Fthat.
OL,17,F"We believe that we have not done
OL,18,Fanything wrong, so we go to an
OL,19,Findependent panel and we are going to
OL,20,Fwait."
