OL,3,CWhat are the charges against
OL,4,CManchester City and what is at stake?
OL,6,FHow long will all this take?
OL,8,FThe hearing is widely reported to be
OL,9,Fscheduled for 10 weeks, with the
OL,10,Fcommission's outcome to follow early
OL,11,Fnext year.
OL,13,FIn the likely event of an appeal, the
OL,14,Ffinal decision may not be handed down
OL,15,Flong before the current season ends.
